           move      07                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      20                   to   v-lto                  .
           move      75                   to   v-pto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Titolo                                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
