           move      06                   to   v-car                  .
           move      05                   to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "BD"                 to   v-edm                  .
           add       12
                     w-vpl-ctr-001    giving   v-lin                  .
           move      20                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-vpl-cdc-vpl
                    (w-vpl-ctr-001)       to   v-num                  .
