                     go to buf-rig-bfo-500.
       buf-rig-bfo-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura sequenziale file [bfr]                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/bfo/fls/ioc/obj/iofbfr"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
