      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to buf-rig-bfo-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test sul massimo                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-bfr-num-prt       not  = w-buf-rig-bfo-prt
                     go to buf-rig-bfo-500.
       buf-rig-bfo-205.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
