      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-rig-snx-mag (1)      .
           go to     car-rig-cat-760.
       car-rig-cat-754.
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
      *                                  * Tipo magazzino : Materia    *
      *                                  * prima                       *
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
           move      "S"                  to   w-rig-snx-mag (1)      .
           go to     car-rig-cat-760.
       car-rig-cat-756.
      *                                  *-----------------------------*
