      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     car-rig-cat-100.
       car-rig-cat-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     car-rig-cat-999.
       car-rig-cat-900.
